to Grammy, please?

02:46.570 --> 02:49.874
-CHILD: I want Daddy.
-Ca-- Cameron?

02:51.642 --> 02:54.342
-Hey, Cam?
-CHILD: Where's Daddy?

02:54.411 --> 02:57.247
-DAPHNE SULLIVAN: Cameron?
-CHILD: Daddy.

02:57.316 --> 02:58.617
DAPHNE: Cameron!

02:59.884 --> 03:00.920
(SIGHS)

03:03.054 --> 03:04.252
DAPHNE: He wants to talk to you.

03:04.321 --> 03:07.288
CAMERON SULLIVAN: Yeah. Oh.
Hey, buddy. How are you?

03:07.357 --> 03:08.424
-CHILD: Good!
-DAPHNE: We love you.

03:08.493 --> 03:09.694
We'll see you tomorrow!

03:14.298 --> 03:16.368
-♪ (SONG FADES) ♪
-I'm gonna help you.

03:17.468 --> 03:18.971
