05:16.520 --> 05:22.358
(IN ENGLISH) Here she is.
The new diva of Palermo.

05:22.427 --> 05:23.858
(CHUCKLES)

05:23.927 --> 05:27.162
-Do you want some coffee?
-I'd love some. Thanks.

05:27.231 --> 05:29.498
-Hugo.
-TANYA MCQUOID-HUNT: Okay.

05:29.567 --> 05:35.604
So, how was Niccolò?

05:35.673 --> 05:38.773
I-- I mean, the whole night
was like a dream.

05:38.842 --> 05:42.044
We just wanted you
to have the perfect send-off.

05:42.113 --> 05:44.212
Oh, send-off. What?

05:44.281 --> 05:47.886
We have to leave Villa Pisano
and bring you back to Taormina.

05:48.152 --> 05:49.351
Oh.

05:49.420 --> 05:51.452
You know, I just wish
I could grab you all

05:51.521 --> 05:53.989
and fold you up in my trunk
and take you with me.

05:54.058 --> 05:55.624
-GROUP: Aww.
-TANYA: I do.

05:55.693 --> 05:57.392
Well, we could probably all fit.

05:57.461 --> 05:58.559
-(CHUCKLES)
-(QUENTIN CHUCKLES)

05:58.628 --> 06:00.630
-(ALL CHUCKLE)
-(TANYA CHUCKLES) That's true.

06:00.699 --> 06:03.231
It's a wonderful thing
to make a--

06:03.300 --> 06:05.637
a new friend so late in life.

06:07.237 --> 06:08.573
Late in life? (CHUCKLES)

06:11.609 --> 06:14.643
It's-- it's a French saying.
"Tard dans la vie."

06:14.712 --> 06:16.679
-Oh.
-Late. Yes, it's, a--

06:16.748 --> 06:17.979
-TANYA: Oh, okay.
-French.

06:18.048 --> 06:20.452
-DIDIER: French saying.
-So many French sayings.

06:21.418 --> 06:24.219
Hey, has anyone seen Portia?

06:24.288 --> 06:25.387
-Is she here?
-No.

06:25.456 --> 06:26.688
TANYA: Did anyone see her
at the party?

06:26.757 --> 06:28.524
She's probably traipsing
through the fields

06:28.593 --> 06:29.857
with Jack somewhere.

06:29.926 --> 06:33.429
This is my luck, you know?
My bad luck with assistants.

06:33.498 --> 06:35.797
They become my boss.

06:35.866 --> 06:39.100
I'm taking orders from them
and they're bossing me around.

06:39.169 --> 06:42.504
And they, you know,
start stealing my medications

06:42.573 --> 06:45.440
and-- and then they disappear.

06:45.509 --> 06:47.709
This is just how it goes
with me.

06:47.778 --> 06:51.411
-(SEAGULLS SQUAWKING)
-♪ (MYSTERIOUS MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

06:57.356 --> 06:58.657
(SIGHS)

07:05.864 --> 07:06.899
(GROANS)

07:12.837 --> 07:13.872
(GROANS)

07:19.210 --> 07:21.243
♪ (MUSIC FADES) ♪

07:21.312 --> 07:22.443
What are you doing?

07:22.512 --> 07:25.381
I-- I can't find my phone.
Where's my phone?

07:25.450 --> 07:26.547
How should I know?

07:26.616 --> 07:28.950
Well, I was charging it
all night.

07:29.019 --> 07:29.885
It was right here.

07:29.954 --> 07:31.052
-So I--
-JACK: I'm sure you'll find it.

07:31.121 --> 07:32.888
It's gotta be somewhere.
Just come back to bed.

07:32.957 --> 07:35.456
I need my phone.
I need to call Tanya.

07:35.525 --> 07:37.997
It's fine. I texted my uncle.

07:41.131 --> 07:43.135
It's all good. (EXHALES)

07:46.170 --> 07:50.372
-Come on. (GROANS)
-(SIGHS)

07:50.441 --> 07:53.542
(EXHALES DEEPLY)
It's all gonna be fine.

07:53.611 --> 07:56.781
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

07:58.277 --> 08:00.219
My phone, it's so weird.
(CHUCKLES)

08:02.386 --> 08:04.156
Maybe you left it at the bar.

08:07.325 --> 08:10.725
No, I definitely had it
last night

08:10.794 --> 08:13.629
'cause I was trying to find you
on Instagram

08:13.698 --> 08:15.134
and I couldn't find you.

08:17.062 --> 08:18.498
I don't do that shit.

08:20.304 --> 08:21.673
Not even Instagram?

08:30.481 --> 08:35.145
-(GROANS)
-(BREATHES DEEPLY)

08:35.214 --> 08:41.026
♪ (INTRIGUING MUSIC PLAYING) ♪

08:50.601 --> 08:52.204
