-(DOOR UNLOCKING)

08:53.170 --> 08:54.136
(DOOR OPENING)

08:54.205 --> 08:56.405
VALENTINA: Oh, Dio.
Buongiorno. (PANTS)

08:56.474 --> 09:01.113
